name: Forest products removal, per ha
description_updated: Total annual value of forest products in current USD per hectares, including both wood and non-wood removal during that year.

name: Hourly compensation
description_updated: Amount of financial compensation for each non-working hour, counted by US$.

name: Extreme temperature affected
description_updated: Total number of people getting affected, injured or killed in extreme temperature during the given year.

name: Life expectancy
description_updated: The average number of years a newborn child would live if current mortality patterns were to stay the same.

name: Income per person
description_updated: Gross domestic product per person adjusted for differences in purchasing power (in international dollars, fixed 2005 prices, PPP based on 2005 ICP).
